<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I have the alakazam site bookmarked and it's a good site for the rune side.  So is the Eq site.  However what good are the runes once you succeed?  What I'd really like to know is how do you research spells?  Are you limited to finding pages and combining them to make spells or can you research most of the spells that otherwise you have to buy?  Like for instance Breeze.  It's only available where most of us are KOS, can we research this spell?<hr>Bondil the Enchanter<br>
Charlene the Pally<br>
