<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5" align="CENTER">
<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">The Practice Runes are used only to increase your skill in research. The only way to get the research spells is to find the pages, or part of pages, that apply to a particular spell, and then combine them in your book.  There is no way to research all the spells, only two or three per level.  But, I believe that Breeze is available on the good side of Kunark also (Firiona Vie), and it is cheaper than the bad side.  The only down side to this is it is a longer trip if you are in Antonica.  Otherwise you will just have to auction for the pages/spells that you need.  Personnally I bought Breeze before I turned 16 when I saw someone auction it. Good luck<hr>Tychor<br>
Enchanter<br>
Druzzil Ro</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
